opensalestax-for-woocommerce — dual license declaration
=====================================================

This software is distributed under your choice of either:

* Apache License, Version 2.0 (Apache-2.0)
  — see ``LICENSE-APACHE.txt``, OR
* GNU General Public License, version 2 or later
  (GPL-2.0-or-later) — see ``LICENSE-GPL.txt``.

SPDX expression: ``Apache-2.0 OR GPL-2.0-or-later``.

Recipient picks. Most consumers — including merchants embedding
the plugin in their own WooCommerce deployment — will find
Apache-2.0 sufficient. The GPL-2.0-or-later option exists so
the plugin can be redistributed via the WordPress.org plugin
directory (whose guidelines require GPL-2.0-or-later or a
compatible license) and to make the dual-license footprint
consistent across the broader OpenSalesTax portfolio (the Odoo
connector, for example, ships LGPL-3.0-or-later OR
AGPL-3.0-or-later for the same cross-ecosystem reasons).

Contributors agree their contributions are licensed under both
options (see ``CONTRIBUTING.md``).

